          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzBAsauUZeZJNRWMyXY9i2FcvndSaZ4jVQPu4PlGHPWv-1iuFM_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I had such a wonderful experience with Dr. Syed and the entire team at Tend Dental. My procedure was seamless and completely painless. Dr. Syed made me feel so comfortable throughout and provided exceptional care from start to finish.\n\nA special thank you to Candice, the office manager, Melly, the dental assistant, and Vrisha at the welcome bar, who ensured a quick and efficient checkout. The entire team is professional, attentive, and truly dedicated to patient care.\n\nI will absolutely be returning again and again. Highly recommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aSlNWQXRZWE5NTVVOcmNFOWlRbnBaWlMxWllVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x57264486ec4db353!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnZJSVAtYXNMMUNrcE9iQnpZZS1ZYUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "2 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-03-26T22:37:44+00:00"
