        {
          "username": "GrannieMe (GrannieMercy)",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "117002210767868782336",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTCg2Zen_FJyzbcrAwRpFbgbGPw9acTU47aK4fAm9GzocBtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Tend at Rockefeller Center is a fantastic practice. It is clean, comfortable, and well run. The dentist took the time to clearly explain everything, which I really appreciated.\n\nBut the biggest kudos go to Therin at the front desk. She is so kind and friendly that you immediately feel welcome and like you matter. She made the experience seamless, from check-in to insurance, payments and scheduling follow-ups. Let's face it: going to the dentist isn't always fun, but she set a tone that was calm and peaceful and that made a difference.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25keVpuWTNkbVU0T1Vkc2VrSmlVR0pzTnpVek9VRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x57264486ec4db353!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOndyZnY3dmU4OUdsekJiUGJsNzUzOUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
