        {
          "username": "Marium",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "114455758052924564196",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1ygFIgI3M_UTvWEV5cVG3C5P7f15qFhUw38hLNei5RTwUSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I had a great time during my appointment at Tend. I love that the office is set up nicely and received a friendly greeting from the front desk as soon I walked in. Dr. Sabrina Syed was incredibly kind and took the time to explain my treatment plan, which I really appreciated. She\u2019s very patient and made the visit feel calm and stress-free.\nOverall, it was a positive experience since visiting the dentist. I would definitely recommend this office to anyone looking for quality dental care!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCQlluWjZja3BQYWpkcWRTMXRURzFoVTFSSVdWRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x57264486ec4db353!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjBBYnZ6ckpPajdqdS1tTG1hU1RIWVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
