          "description": "I was a first time patient here & I had an amazing expirience. I was in a lot of dental pain on a friday afternoon and they were able to see me as an emergency. I saw Dr. syed,  she was so kind and helped me resolve my dental pain. I had an extraction same day and it was completley pain free. Her bedside manner was so comforting, i definitley recommend and will be going back for my recare appointments! 10/10 reccommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNVV6bG5UbmxaVFdkWVVtdDZkMWhYWm1wYVFsRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x57264486ec4db353!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjk5UzlnTnlZTWdYUmt6d1hXZmpaQlE%7C%7C?hl=en",
