          "description": "I came to Tend for a whitening treatment, and I was truly impressed by this dental office. The staff was incredibly friendly and accommodating, and they even provided a toiletry kit so I could brush my teeth before the appointment. My hygienist, Katrina, performed both the cleaning and whitening treatment, and she made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire process. I can honestly say it was the most painless cleaning I\u2019ve ever had. My teeth looked so much brighter thanks to the treatment!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sb1l6aHJUSEZoYzA1dFQxUjNiM0F4TUVwTk9WRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x57264486ec4db353!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmloYzhrTHFhc05tT1R3b3AxMEpNOVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
